C1.1 An outdoor living area is to be provided:
i. of a minimum 30 sqm for R20 sites and 32 sqm for R30 sites;
ii. behind the street setback area;
iii. directly accessible from the primary living space of the dwelling;
iv. with a minimum length and width dimension of 4m; and
v. with at least two-thirds of the required area without permanent roof cover.
(Refer Figure 13 of the R-Codes)
